description: The foodies of Orlando are going starry-eyed for the delightfully tasty gourmet hot dogs & sausages from Astro Dawgz. The team at this trailer is taking their specialty dawgz and topping them with high-quality options like homemade chili, creamy pub cheese, savory sautéed onions, cherry-smoked bacon, mac ‘n cheese, ranch mashed potatoes, and more, all to guarantee that your every bite will be packed with flavor that is “out of this world”!You just gotta try Astro Dawgz for deliciousness that will keep you coming back.
name: Astro Dawgz
